  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they take me to the hospital that was, uh, near to the front, they ma-- they no cleaned up my wounds, and they begin to send s-- send me in the other hospital-- bigger hospitals.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they take me through-- maybe I went through six or seven hospitals--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they send me far away from the front.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Far away-- that's in [INAUDIBLE] [? republic. ?] And in all the hospitals, I was for, uh, six, seven months, I was in hospitals.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They want to take off my foot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, people, they was a couple times wounded, they told me, don't give it to take off the foot, because it's very easy for the-- for the doctors in-- to cut off in we young people-- and two weeks, three weeks, that's all.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No, you will not have a foot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't-- I, uh, listened to the-- to the good advice from the, uh, people was-- they was a couple times wounded, and I didn't give, uh, to take off my foot.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How it-- it was bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was-- with my foot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it's come maybe-- and I was in the hospital until 1945.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "By approximately March, they send me out from the hospital on crutches.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then become a more worse problem I got.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The time-- everybody from the war, they got families, most of the Ukraine people had families, somebody was waiting for-- for somebody will come from the-- from the-- from the war.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't have to whom, where to go, and where to leave-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember, they gave me from the hospital, they gave me a couple of rubles for a time-- I was a partisan.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Uh, in somethings they give me some pension.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "No-- it's nothing to do, it was a very little, no.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
